headline: US Financial 15 Split Corp. Preferred Dividend Declared
summary: TORONTO, Feb. 19, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- US Financial 15 Split Corp ("US Financial 15") declares its monthly distribution of $0.07275 for each Preferred share, or 10.00% annually based on the previous month end net asset value. Distributions are payable March 10, 2026 to shareholders on record as at February 27, 2026. headline: Ultra-rich families spend more on their private investment firms as their fortunes rise
summary: Family offices with at least $1 billion in assets reported spending $6.6 million in annual operating costs on average, according to J.P. Morgan Private Bank.
